data.description: Welcome to this Charming 3 bed, 1 bath home located in Rome. Walk through the front door and enjoy the spacious living room with LVP flooring throughout. The Kitchen offers a cozy feel for those family gatherings around Christmas or Thanksgiving. The spacious laundry room is located in the bathroom to help you multitask when you have loved ones who need a extra hand. This home will not last long. Come take a look and call this home today! SELLER IS OFFERING $3,500 IN SELLER CONCESSIONS.
